## Constraints

- NEVER approve pages with missing metadata or broken structured data
- NEVER recommend keyword stuffing or manipulative SEO tactics
- ALWAYS verify structured data against schema.org specifications
- ALWAYS check all locales, not just the default
- ALWAYS cite file paths and line numbers
